OL,3,CBBC Breakfast boss takes extended
OL,4,Cleave over bullying claims
OL,6,FBBC Breakfast editor Richard Frediani
OL,7,Fis to take an extended period of leave
OL,8,Fafter bullying allegations were made
OL,9,Fagainst him.
OL,11,FIt comes after industry publication
OL,12,FDeadline reported complaints over Mr
OL,13,FFrediani's conduct. Allegations
OL,14,Freported by Deadline included shouting
OL,15,Fand swearing at colleagues. The
OL,16,Fpublication also reported that a woman
OL,17,Fhad her grievance upheld after
OL,18,Fclaiming that Mr Frediani physically
OL,19,Fshook her in the newsroom.
