OL,6,FMedia outlets also reported that an
OL,7,Finternal investigation is being
OL,8,Fcarried out into the allegations. A
OL,9,FBBC spokesperson said: "While we do
OL,10,Fnot comment on individual cases, we
OL,11,Ftake all complaints about conduct at
OL,12,Fwork extremely seriously and will not
OL,13,Ftolerate behaviour that is not in line
OL,14,Fwith our values.
OL,16,F"We have robust processes in place and
OL,17,Fwould encourage any staff with
OL,18,Fconcerns to raise them directly with
OL,19,Fus so they can be addressed."
