OL,3,CBBC Breakfast boss takes extended
OL,4,Cleave over bullying claims
OL,6,FBBC News reported that an HR advisor
OL,7,Ffrom the consultancy firm PwC has been
OL,8,Fbrought in to support the BBC's
OL,9,Finvestigation into the culture of the
OL,10,Fbroadcaster's flagship morning
OL,11,Fprogramme.
OL,13,FPwC has declined to comment.
OL,15,FMr Frediani joined the award-winning
OL,16,Fshow, produced in Salford, in 2019.
OL,17,FHis role was later extended to
OL,18,Fproducing News at One last year.
