OL,3,CBBC Breakfast boss takes extended
OL,4,Cleave over bullying claims
OL,6,FBefore joining the BBC, Mr Frediani
OL,7,Fworked for ITN, where he held senior
OL,8,Froles on the team that produces ITV
OL,9,FNews.
OL,11,FHe accepted the Bafta Award in May for
OL,12,Fbest TV news coverage of the Post
OL,13,FOffice scandal.
OL,15,FIn April an independent review into
OL,16,Fthe BBC found there was not a "toxic
OL,17,Fculture" but reforms where needed to
OL,18,Ftake quicker action against staff who
OL,19,Fstep out of line.
