OL,6,FAt the time BBC chairman Samir Shah
OL,7,Ftold presenters: "After today, let me
OL,8,Fstate it clearly, if you think you're
OL,9,Ftoo big a star or too important to
OL,10,Flive by the values of this
OL,11,Forganisation, not only are you wrong,
OL,12,Fbut we will find you out."
OL,14,FHe also said he would draw "a line in
OL,15,Fthe sand".
OL,17,FITV News has approached the BBC and Mr
OL,18,FFrediani for comment.
